item.title: Re: Emo Level 2 Season 1
item.content:encoded: You need to be second to do the 'Rock the World' A-side. Really, it's up to chance. It'd probably be better just to do the B-side variant, which need 20 CDs instead of 10 CDs and ranked second.

item.title: Emo Level 2 Season 1
item.content:encoded: Does anyone have any tips in order to attempt to get ranked second as a Season 1? Currently a Legacy Jounin, wondering how high I should attempt to get my ranking to come second (Something tells me that it's mostly down to chance but meh). If anyone has any idea on what day would be best and roughly how high to get my rankings it'd be appreciated.
